    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Support the Ministry of Women , Children and Social Welfare to prepare  its sixth CEDAW periodic report\r\n\r\nSupport civil society groups to  draft a comprehensive CEDAW shadow report taking into account the Beijing + 20 process and the post 2015 discussions and UPR shadow report\r\n\r\nFinalise and implement the Action Plan for Beijing+20 Review in collaboration with BBC and NNBN networks, CSOs and the Government:\r\n* Support the review planning and preparation for the CSW59 on Beijing+20\r\n* Support Government and CSO participation at the 59th CSW session on Beijing +20 and reporting back post CSW59 at the national level\r\n* Support the post-CSW59 debfriefing and follow up on conclusions with Government and CSO stakeholders at the national level\r\n* In collaboration with Media Advisory Group (MAG), undertake pre-CSW59 media monitoring and submit monthly stories to media houses post-CSW59"
      },
      "ne": null
    },
